# AibriefAI Zero-Cost Render Launch

## Stack

| Layer | Service | Cost |
|---|---|---:|
| Static hosting | Render Static Site free tier | $0.00 |
| Primary LLM | Google Gemini API free tier | $0.00 |
| Fallback LLM | Groq Llama 3.3 70B free tier | $0.00 |
| Pipeline | GitHub Actions scheduled workflow | $0.00 |
| Data | HN Firebase, arXiv, GitHub, Reddit | $0.00 |
| Monitoring | UptimeRobot + Sentry free tier | $0.00 |
| Domain | `aibriefai.onrender.com` | $0.00 |

## Render deployment

```bash
git add .
git commit -m "Launch AibriefAI zero-cost Render stack"
git push origin main
```

Render Dashboard:

```text
New → Static Site → Connect GitHub repo → Use render.yaml → Create Static Site
```

Expected URL:

```text
https://aibriefai.onrender.com
```

Verify:

```bash
curl -I https://aibriefai.onrender.com
curl -fsS https://aibriefai.onrender.com/health
curl -fsS https://aibriefai.onrender.com/data/signals.json | python -m json.tool >/dev/null
```

## GitHub Actions secrets

```bash
gh secret set GEMINI_API_KEY
gh secret set GROQ_API_KEY
gh secret set SENTRY_DSN
gh secret set GITHUB_TOKEN

gh variable set GEMINI_MODEL --body gemini-2.5-flash
gh variable set GROQ_MODEL --body llama-3.3-70b-versatile
```

No key is required to launch. Missing LLM keys trigger rule-based fallback.

## UptimeRobot monitor

Import or manually create:

```text
Monitor type: HTTP(s)
URL: https://aibriefai.onrender.com/health
Interval: 5 minutes
Expected status: 200
Alert contact: Fmg_511@hotmail.com
```

Config file:

```text
infra/monitoring/uptimerobot/aibriefai-monitor.json
```
